The paper deals with interactive segmentation using deep neural networks, which is a topic that falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The proposed method involves optimization and refinement, which are common themes in machine learning (cs.LG). The experiments involve datasets and evaluation metrics commonly used in computer graphics (cs.GR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
